    <section class="top-section">
        <h1>Beagle</h1>
        <p>
            The <strong>Beagle</strong> is a breed of small hound, similar in appearance to the much larger foxhound.
            The Beagle is a scent hound, developed primarily for hunting hare.
        </p>
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beagle" target="_blank">Read More</a>
    </section>

