    <!-- Trivia Section -->
    <section class="trivia-section">
        <h2>Trivia</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Dogs of the Beagle breed are known for their <strong>friendly</strong> and <strong>curious</strong> nature.</li>
            <li>The Beagle is a <em>scent hound</em> and has an excellent sense of smell.</li>
            <li>Beagles are often used in <strong>lab experiments</strong> due to their size and calm temperament.</li>
        </ol>
